#   - Updated domain constraint to accept single string OR array (multi-domain support)
#   - Domain values reference M1_Domains.jsonld (evolving registry)
#   - Added comprehensive domain examples in validation message
#   - Updated all statistics and documentation to reflect m1:domain
#
# v1.0 (2026-04-13): FINAL grammar after complete corpus analysis (100% coverage)
#   - Complete corpus: 24 Poclets + 2 other instances (26 total)
#   - Added support for 3 instance types (Poclet, SystemicFramework, SymbolicSystemGrammar)
#   - Identified m3:ontologyCategory violation (VSM) - obsolete, use m3:ontologyType
#   - Identified ORIVE terminology violation (VSM) - obsolete, use REVOI
#   - Updated all statistics based on 26 instances
#   - m2:changelog reached 69% global (71% poclets-only - threshold reached)
#   - rdfs:label reached 73% global (71% poclets-only - threshold maintained)
#   - Final forbidden patterns count: 10 patterns to eliminate
#   - Documented complete conformance levels per constraint
#
